account.descriptionLink:
Proposal to license all experimental data generated by pump.science, including IP held by Urolithin A holders (e.g., C. elegans, flies, and future data), to Noumenon Association (Chemiax). In exchange, Chemiax will pay 15% of royalties from sales, used exclusively for buyback and burn of the URO token (FvgqHMfL9yn39V79huDPy3YUNDoYJpuLWng2JfmQpump) via the Raydium pool (3hsdbMFsiCh3YCsXoFjgx4TVpxECsUE9nRMgvaoyveQT).

A simple majority is required to pass, with no quorum requirements.
account.name: Licensing Urolithin A Data to Noumenon Association (Chemiax)
